scene.message:
Ms. Natsumi: Hey, Nanjo!{nl}
Take off that bandage and{nl}
the wound will reopen!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: No need to worry.{nl}
Wrapped like this, the{nl}
bandage is meaningless anyway.{waitkey}{ret}

Ms. Natsumi: Take your{nl}
leave...?{wait_fr:32} You're not{nl}
planning to go outside?{waitkey}{ret}

Student: That's right, Nanjo.{nl}
You'll just get hurt again.{nl}
Besides...{waitkey}{clearbox}we all searched everywhere,{nl}
but it seems we can't leave{nl}
the school...{waitkey}There's no exit anywhere!!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Hm?{waitkey}You're not making sense.{nl}
Save the nonsense for{nl}
your dreams.{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: It's not nonsense!{nl}
It's true!! The Snow Queen{nl}
trapped us in here!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: The Snow Queen?{waitkey}Is it April Fools' today?{nl}
Come up with a better lie.{waitkey}{clearbox}I've no time to humor fools.{nl}
Move aside.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Mayuzumi, you too{wait_fr:32}...{wait_fr:32}...{wait_fr:32}{nl}
It can't be!!{waitkey}The school, like{nl}
the hospital?!{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: Regrettably,{nl}
it is exactly that.{waitkey}{clearbox}If I must name a difference,{nl}
there are no Demons this{nl}
time - but no exit, either.{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: Yeah,{nl}
same as the hospital.{waitkey}{clearbox}If there's a difference, no{nl}
demons wandering this time -{nl}
but no exit instead.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: ......{waitkey}I'm worried about Inaba{nl}
and Sonomura. I must get{nl}
outside no matter what.{waitkey}{ret}

Maki's Mother: Maki...{waitkey}{clearbox}Can we really not leave?{nl}
Is there no way at all{nl}
to get outside?{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Hm, I understand.{waitkey}{clearbox}If we save Ms. Saeko from{nl}
this Snow Queen, the school{nl}
returns to normal.{waitkey}{ret}

Don't tell me you want{nl}
my help?{nl}
{ctl0e:7}{ret}

Nanjo: Fine.{waitkey}{clearbox}If you insist that much,{nl}
I suppose I could help.{waitkey}Pursuing Sonomura and the{nl}
others comes after.{waitkey}{ret}
